snippet.title: Is it okay to pee in the shower? (Don't be afraid)
snippet.description:
Try it tonight :)

I make all of my charts from scratch with open data sets. Here's where I got the shower pee habits data (Cards Against Humanity): https://www.kaggle.com/somesnm/partyn...
Music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X8yPK1Q_IiI

SMASH that like button and subscribe if you like my videos! I try to get creative with the data that I find and try to tell a story with it. 
 
If you're new to my channel, I do data storytelling :) Hope you enjoyed! -
